The paper also discusses the impact of social welfare, which falls under the domain of cryptography and security, making cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) another likely sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the impact of bundling on profit, which falls under the domain of multimedia, making cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible sub-category.
